channel.title: Can't set my server IP in my Client
channel.description:
Well, my client I downloaded and I am going to use is NOT one of the IP changer ones. In fact, it is Kihomura's client that he released like, 1/2 years ago?
Anyways, my problem is that it doesn't have an EGUI or Gui, and I can't figure out the class in which the server IP resides. I have tried the client class, and I'm not sure if that's it because I typed 127.0.0.1 and it didn't come up.
I know this means that 127.0.0.1 is either not the IP already set in the client, or that I'm in the wrong class. Anyone have any ideas?
